casebody.data:
Macdonald et al., Appellants, v. Wallstein et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. May 9, 1890.)

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

Blumenstiel & Hirseh, for appellants. Benno Loewy, for respondents.

No opinion. Motion denied, without costs.
